cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper focuses on the threat of adversarial attacks on deep learning in Computer Vision, which suggests that cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of deep neural networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also analyzes the existence of adversarial attacks, which falls under cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). Finally, the paper proposes defenses against adversarial attacks, which falls under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
